m_q.target_metric: Determine if 'Other' reports exceeded 50% of total reports in any year from 2001-2024
sub_questions: Calculate total reports per year (Fraud + Identity Theft + Other)
Calculate the proportion of Other reports to total reports for each year
Check if any year has Other proportion > 0.5

format_notes: All numeric columns are integer type
Data spans years 2001-2020 in the sample shown

constraints: Year must be between 2001 and 2024 inclusive
All report counts (Fraud, Identity Theft, Other) must be non-negative
derived_filters: Calculate Total = Fraud + Identity Theft + Other
output_format_requirements: No explanation or additional text required
